{{!
    @template totara_msteams/listbox

    This template generates a list box that looks like the drop down list component of MS Teams.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * id: the unique id
    * name: the field name
    * label: the label text
    * errortext: the error text when validation failed
    * placeholder: the place holder text
    * required: set true to make the field mandatory
    * search: set true to drop a magnify icon (required must be false)
    * autofocus: set true to add the autofocus attribute
    * spinner: the template data of totara_msteams/spinner

    Example content (json):
    {
        "idlist": "msteams-13579",
        "idlabel": "msteams-24680",
        "label": "Select item",
        "spinner": {
            "fullscreen": false,
            "label": "Loading..."
        }
    }
}}

<div class="accesshide" id="{{idlabel}}">{{label}}</div>
<ul class="totara_msteams_form__list__items" tabindex="0" role="listbox" id="{{idlist}}" aria-labelledby="{{idlabel}}">
    {{#spinner}}<li role="presentation" class="totara_msteams_form__list__spinner">{{> totara_msteams/spinner }}</li>{{/spinner}}
</ul>
